19#include "QRFinderPattern.h"
20
21namespace ZXing {
22namespace QRCode {
23
24/**
25* <p>Encapsulates information about finder patterns in an image, including the location of
26* the three finder patterns, and their estimated module size.</p>
27*
28* @author Sean Owen
29*/
30class FinderPatternInfo
31{
32public:
33 FinderPattern bottomLeft;
34 FinderPattern topLeft;
35 FinderPattern topRight;
36
37 bool isValid() const { return bottomLeft.isValid() && topLeft.isValid() && topRight.isValid(); }
38};
39
40} // QRCode
41} // ZXing
